Customer Decile Analysis and Cohort Analysis
Kabduali Ayaulym

Data cleaning and preparation for analysis
Customer segmentation using deciles
Calculation of key metrics: revenue, profit, average order value (AOV), average order frequency (AOF), and % active customers
Creation of charts, tables, and visualizations to summarize customer behavior
Interpretation of results to identify high-value and low-value customer segments
Translating quantitative insights into actionable business recommendations
